title: Thomas Hedger | Balance For Better
body_html:
Balance For Better by Thomas Hedger

This print is part of a limited range curated by artist agency Grand Matter, in collaboration with RoomFifty, to celebrate gender equality and commemorate International Women’s Day 2019. Available for purchase until Sunday 31st March 2019, all profits from sales of the 20 designs in the range will be donated to Women For Refugee Women - a charity doing great work to challenge the injustices experienced by women seeking asylum in the UK.
